sentences: Bruce R. Gaitsch (; born February 7, 1953) is an American guitarist, composer, and producer.
Gaitsch co-wrote the Madonna song "La Isla Bonita", an international #1 single that earned Gaitsch an award from the American Society of Composers, Authors and Publishers in 1987.
